she told the police that she has known senator adams for many 
years as a family friend she said that senator adams made sexual 
overtures toward her for several weeks if not longer 
nevertheless she arranged to have dinner alone with him when he 
did not appear she drove alone to his house arriving after dark 
there she had several drinks and by her account remained in 
