american homes the television and the bible nielsen media 
research said it was developing a passive people meter that 
would actually watch viewers to determine which ones were watching 
what shows and when they left the room franklin computer a mt 
holly nj company unveiled an electronic version of the 
scriptures delivered by a new handheld computer 
